{"tid":2236911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周五繁忙時間派樽 酒吧質疑「做show」","createTime":"2020-10-09T23:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T00:03:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9991afa575d202d892211261d0a8ec44e01115","tid":2236911,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20201010/s00001/1602266688974/%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%94%e7%b9%81%e5%bf%99%e6%99%82%e9%96%93%e6%b4%be%e6%a8%bd-%e9%85%92%e5%90%a7%e8%b3%aa%e7%96%91%e3%80%8c%e5%81%9ashow%e3%80%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201010%2Fs00001%2F1602266688974%2F%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25ba%2594%25e7%25b9%2581%25e5%25bf%2599%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2596%2593%25e6%25b4%25be%25e6%25a8%25bd-%25e9%2585%2592%25e5%2590%25a7%25e8%25b3%25aa%25e7%2596%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2581%259ashow%25e3%2580%258d&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=36599af7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201010%2Fs00001%2F1602266688974%2F%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25ba%2594%25e7%25b9%2581%25e5%25bf%2599%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2596%2593%25e6%25b4%25be%25e6%25a8%25bd-%25e9%2585%2592%25e5%2590%25a7%25e8%25b3%25aa%25e7%2596%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2581%259ashow%25e3%2580%258d&h=038776df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20201010/s00001/1602266688974/%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%94%e7%b9%81%e5%bf%99%e6%99%82%e9%96%93%e6%b4%be%e6%a8%bd-%e9%85%92%e5%90%a7%e8%b3%aa%e7%96%91%e3%80%8c%e5%81%9ashow%e3%80%8d</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】食環署昨起一連3晚安排檢測承辦商前往酒吧區設流動檢測車派發樣本瓶，承辦商人員昨晚先到人頭湧湧的中環蘭桂坊派樽，有酒吧負責人質疑在酒吧忙於工作之時派樽是「做show」，又指員工每日都接觸顧客，質疑檢測成效。<br />\n<br />\n檢測承辦商Prenetics的流動檢測車輛昨傍晚在雲咸街附近停泊，有職員下車向酒吧職員及顧客派樣本包，鼓勵他們自願檢測。Prenetics行政總裁楊聖武說預備了1000個樣本包，今天會回來收集，市民亦可往鰂魚涌收集點交樣本。港大微生學系講座教授袁國勇昨晚亦現身蘭桂坊觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有雲咸街的酒吧負責人收到樣本包後，說會分發給員工，但不會強制員工檢測。他質疑為何要選酒吧最繁忙的周五晚派樽，質疑是「做show」，又認為員工每日都接觸顧客，質疑檢測成效，「今日無事，唔代表聽日無事」。他認為更重要是自己做好防疫措施。</strong><br />\n<br />\n質疑成效：今日無事唔代表聽日<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘭桂坊集團主席盛智文稱，如每次疫情爆發便關酒吧，業界難以生存。他建議如個別酒吧出現個案，有關酒吧應先停業，為員工檢測及徹底消毒。另外，他認為在酒吧區設流動檢測車是好主意，鼓勵員工交樣本，認為有助控疫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盲都知呢單野係官商勾結"},{"pid":"983bddecf90296d8759b3f6b714e7b89e909a65c","tid":2236911,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"轉頭喺街頭街尾啲垃圾桶可以回收番啲樽"},{"pid":"05046c855085b20348a66a3998eb36d66e95c4d1","tid":2236911,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"983bddecf90296d8759b3f6b714e7b89e909a65c","tid":2236911,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"轉頭喺街頭街尾啲垃圾桶可以回收番啲樽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T00:03:48.000Z","msg":"仲要有篤數前科<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/SZKWFEKCZVGQFAMC7M2RGY5Y7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FSZKWFEKCZVGQFAMC7M2RGY5Y7I%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=bf3b99dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FSZKWFEKCZVGQFAMC7M2RGY5Y7I%2F&h=1c01e8f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/SZKWFEKCZVGQFAMC7M2RGY5Y7I/</a>"}]}